name: Beef Wellington
description: A classic Australian dish featuring a tender beef fillet coated with pâté and mushrooms, wrapped in puff pastry and baked to perfection.

name: Barramundi Fillet with Lemon Butter Sauce
description: A delicious Australian seafood dish, the barramundi fillet is pan - seared and topped with a zesty lemon butter sauce.

name: Kangaroo Steak
description: An Australian specialty, kangaroo steak offers a lean and gamey meat with a unique flavor, cooked to your preferred doneness.

name: Meat Pie
description: A staple of Australian cuisine, this savory pie is filled with minced meat and gravy, encased in a flaky pastry crust.

name: Lamington
description: A popular Australian dessert, lamingtons are sponge cakes coated in chocolate sauce and desiccated coconut.

name: Pavlova
description: A meringue - based dessert, pavlova has a crisp crust and a soft, marshmallow - like center, topped with fresh fruits and whipped cream.

name: Chicken Parmigiana
description: An Australian favorite, chicken parmigiana consists of a breaded chicken cutlet topped with tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, and baked until bubbly.

name: Seafood Paella
description: A rich and flavorful Australian dish, paella is a rice dish cooked with a variety of fresh seafood, spices, and saffron.

name: Spicy Australian Prawn Curry
description: This Australian prawn curry is a spicy and aromatic dish, with succulent prawns cooked in a curry sauce with local spices.

name: Vegetable and Feta Quiche
description: A savory Australian quiche filled with a mixture of vegetables and feta cheese, baked in a buttery pastry crust.

name: Mapo Tofu
description: A famous Chinese dish from Sichuan cuisine, mapo tofu features soft tofu in a spicy and numbing sauce made with minced meat and Sichuan peppercorns.

name: Kung Pao Chicken
description: A classic Chinese stir - fry, kung pao chicken combines diced chicken, peanuts, vegetables, and a spicy sauce for a flavorful dish.

name: Sweet and Sour Pork
description: A popular Chinese dish, sweet and sour pork consists of deep - fried pork pieces coated in a sweet and tangy sauce.

name: Beijing Roast Duck
description: A world - renowned Chinese dish, Beijing roast duck is known for its crispy skin and tender meat, usually served with thin pancakes, scallions, and hoisin sauce.

name: Sichuan Hot Pot
description: A communal Chinese dish, Sichuan hot pot features a spicy broth filled with various meats, vegetables, and seafood cooked at the table.

name: Xiaolongbao
description: A type of Chinese steamed dumpling, xiaolongbao are filled with savory meat and a delicious broth, bursting with flavor when bitten into.

name: General Tso's Chicken
description: A well - known Chinese - American dish, General Tso's chicken is deep - fried chicken pieces in a sweet and spicy sauce.

name: Yangzhou Fried Rice
description: A classic Chinese fried rice dish, Yangzhou fried rice is made with eggs, ham, shrimp, vegetables, and fragrant rice.

name: Spicy Dan Dan Noodles
description: A spicy Chinese noodle dish, Dan Dan noodles are topped with minced meat, spicy sauce, and various seasonings.

name: Steamed Fish with Scallions and Ginger
description: A simple yet elegant Chinese dish, steamed fish is seasoned with scallions and ginger, highlighting the freshness of the fish.

name: Caesar Salad
description: A classic Western salad, Caesar salad consists of romaine lettuce, croutons, Parmesan cheese, and a creamy Caesar dressing.

name: Greek Salad
description: A refreshing Western salad, Greek salad features tomatoes, cucumbers, feta cheese, olives, and a light vinaigrette dressing.

name: Caprese Salad
description: A simple and fresh Western salad, Caprese salad combines tomatoes, fresh mozzarella cheese, basil leaves, and a drizzle of balsamic glaze.

name: Cobb Salad
description: A hearty Western salad, Cobb salad includes lettuce, chicken, bacon, eggs, tomatoes, avocado, and blue cheese dressing.

name: Spinach Salad with Warm Bacon Dressing
description: A delicious Western salad, spinach salad is topped with warm bacon dressing, hard - boiled eggs, and other ingredients.

name: Wedge Salad
description: A classic Western salad, wedge salad is a large wedge of iceberg lettuce topped with bacon bits, blue cheese dressing, and other toppings.

name: Spicy Southwest Salad
description: A spicy Western salad, this salad combines ingredients like black beans, corn, tomatoes, and a spicy dressing.

name: Roasted Vegetable Salad
description: A healthy Western salad, roasted vegetable salad features a variety of roasted vegetables, usually served with a light dressing.

name: Seafood Salad
description: A fresh Western salad, seafood salad is made with a combination of seafood such as shrimp, crab, and scallops, and a light dressing.

name: Chicken Caesar Wrap Salad
description: A convenient Western dish, chicken Caesar wrap salad combines chicken, Caesar salad ingredients, and is wrapped in a tortilla.

name: Nigiri Sushi
description: A traditional Japanese sushi, nigiri sushi consists of a slice of raw fish on top of a small mound of vinegared rice.

name: Sashimi Platter
description: A Japanese dish featuring thinly sliced raw fish, sashimi is often served with soy sauce and wasabi.

name: California Roll
description: A popular Japanese - American sushi roll, California roll is made with avocado, cucumber, and imitation crab meat, wrapped in seaweed and rice.

name: Tempura Udon
description: A Japanese noodle dish, tempura udon features thick udon noodles in a savory broth, topped with tempura - fried seafood and vegetables.

name: Miso Ramen
description: A classic Japanese ramen, miso ramen has a rich and savory miso - based broth, usually served with noodles, meat, and other toppings.

name: Yakitori
description: Japanese grilled chicken skewers, yakitori are marinated in a special sauce and grilled to perfection.

name: Spicy Tuna Roll
description: A Japanese sushi roll, spicy tuna roll is filled with spicy tuna and other ingredients, wrapped in seaweed and rice.

name: Teriyaki Chicken Donburi
description: A Japanese rice bowl dish, teriyaki chicken donburi features chicken cooked in a sweet teriyaki sauce, served over a bowl of rice.

name: Okonomiyaki
description: A savory Japanese pancake, okonomiyaki is filled with a variety of ingredients such as cabbage, meat, and seafood, and topped with sauce and mayonnaise.

name: Matcha Mochi
description: A Japanese sweet, matcha mochi is a soft and chewy rice cake filled with sweet red bean paste and flavored with matcha green tea.

name: Tom Yum Goong
description: A famous Thai soup, Tom Yum Goong is a spicy and sour soup made with shrimp, lemongrass, kaffir lime leaves, and other herbs.

name: Pad Thai
description: A popular Thai stir - fried rice noodle dish, Pad Thai is cooked with eggs, tofu, shrimp or chicken, peanuts, and a sweet and savory sauce.

name: Green Curry Chicken
description: A Thai curry dish, green curry chicken is made with chicken, green curry paste, coconut milk, and vegetables.

name: Som Tum
description: A spicy Thai papaya salad, Som Tum is made with shredded papaya, tomatoes, lime juice, fish sauce, and other seasonings.

name: Massaman Curry
description: A Thai curry with a complex flavor, Massaman curry combines elements of Indian and Thai cuisine, featuring meat, potatoes, and a rich curry sauce.

name: Chicken Satay
description: A Thai appetizer, chicken satay consists of grilled chicken skewers served with a peanut dipping sauce.

name: Khao Soi
description: A Thai noodle soup, Khao Soi features egg noodles in a creamy curry broth, topped with crispy noodles and other ingredients.

name: Spicy Basil Chicken
description: A Thai stir - fry dish, spicy basil chicken is made with chicken, fresh basil leaves, and a spicy sauce.

name: Mango Sticky Rice
description: A popular Thai dessert, mango sticky rice combines sweet sticky rice, fresh mangoes, and coconut cream.

name: Tom Kha Gai
description: A Thai soup, Tom Kha Gai is a creamy coconut - based soup with chicken, lemongrass, and kaffir lime leaves.

name: Butter Chicken
description: A well - known Indian dish, butter chicken consists of chicken pieces cooked in a rich and creamy tomato - based sauce.

name: Chicken Tikka Masala
description: A popular Indian dish, chicken tikka masala features marinated and grilled chicken pieces in a spiced tomato - cream sauce.

name: Palak Paneer
description: An Indian vegetarian dish, Palak Paneer is made with spinach puree and paneer cheese, cooked with spices.

name: Biryani
description: A fragrant Indian rice dish, biryani is cooked with long - grain rice, meat or vegetables, and a blend of spices.

name: Samosas
description: A classic Indian snack, samosas are triangular pastries filled with spiced potatoes, peas, and sometimes meat.

name: Chana Masala
description: An Indian chickpea curry, Chana Masala is made with chickpeas in a spicy and flavorful tomato - based sauce.

name: Vada Pav
description: A popular Indian street food, Vada Pav consists of a deep - fried potato fritter sandwiched between a bun, served with chutneys.

name: Rogan Josh
description: A rich and spicy Indian lamb curry, Rogan Josh is made with tender lamb pieces in a flavorful gravy.

name: Dosa
description: A South Indian crepe - like dish, dosa is made from fermented rice and lentil batter, usually served with sambar and chutney.

name: Gulab Jamun
description: A sweet Indian dessert, Gulab Jamun are deep - fried milk balls soaked in a sugary syrup.

name: Bibimbap
description: A traditional Korean dish, Bibimbap is a bowl of rice topped with various vegetables, meat, and a fried egg, mixed with gochujang sauce.

name: Kimchi Jjigae
description: A spicy Korean stew, Kimchi Jjigae is made with fermented kimchi, pork or other meats, and vegetables.

name: Bulgogi
description: A popular Korean barbecue dish, Bulgogi consists of thinly sliced marinated beef, grilled and served with rice and vegetables.

name: Japchae
description: A Korean noodle dish, Japchae features sweet potato noodles stir - fried with vegetables, meat, and a savory sauce.

name: Tteokbokki
description: A well - loved Korean street food, Tteokbokki is made with spicy rice cakes, fish cakes, and other ingredients.

name: Galbi
description: A Korean barbecue dish, Galbi consists of marinated beef short ribs, grilled to perfection.

name: Haemul Pajeon
description: A Korean savory pancake, Haemul Pajeon is made with a batter of flour, eggs, and seafood, cooked on a griddle.

name: Spicy Dakgalbi
description: A spicy Korean chicken dish, Spicy Dakgalbi is made with chicken, vegetables, and a spicy sauce, cooked in a large pan.

name: Manduguk
description: A Korean soup, Manduguk features dumplings in a clear broth, often served on special occasions.

name: Patbingsu
description: A popular Korean dessert, Patbingsu is a shaved ice dessert topped with sweet red beans, fruits, condensed milk, and other toppings.

name: Samgyeopsal
description: A Korean BBQ classic, thick slices of pork belly are grilled on a sizzling iron plate until charred and are often served wrapped with lettuce, garlic and a Korean dipping sauce.
